    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## NOTES:\nAutomates AI video creation from a text idea and then saves the output to Google Drive and logs it in Google Sheets.\n**STEPS:**\n1.Open the Form Trigger URL and submit your video idea\nLLM Chain 1 writes a 10-second video scene from your idea\n2.LLM Chain 2 converts the scene into an AI video prompt\n3.POST Node sends the prompt to MagicHour and gets a video ID\n4.Wait → GET Node → If Node keeps checking every 10 seconds until the video is ready\n5.Once complete, the video is downloaded, saved to Google Drive, and its URL is pasted in Google Sheets",
        "height": 304,
        "width": 640,
        "color": 7
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -2448,
        -304
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "192df850-fadb-466f-8102-a1f589f5c8c1",
      "name": "Sticky Note"
    }
